comments: Rondo (LAL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Randle (NOP) and absorbs the contact.
Kuzma (LAL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Randle (NOP) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Miller (NOP) moves slightly into Ingram's (LAL) path and he makes marginal contact that Ingram is able to move through during his driving shot attempt.
Randle (NOP) slips the pick and makes marginal contact to Ingram (LAL), but does not affect his ability to defend on the play.
James (LAL) makes marginal contact to Holiday's (NOP) front as he dribbles the ball off of his leg.
Ingram (LAL) and Randle (NOP) engage and separate in the lane.
Kuzma (LAL) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Randle (NOP) and absorbs the contact.
Holiday (NOP) maintains a legal guarding position on James (LAL) during the drive.
James (LAL) legally regains control of the ball after it is dislodged by Miller (NOP).
Miller (NOP) makes incidental contact with James (LAL) as he dislodges the ball at the end of James' drive.
James (LAL) extends his leg as part of a natural shooting motion on the jump shot attempt and the contact with Holiday (NOP) is incidental.
Kuzma (LAL) and Miller (NOP) engage and separate.
Randle (NOP) commits a take foul on James (LAL).
[Observable in enhanced video] Payton (NOP) enters the lane before the release of the free throw.
Randle (NOP) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Kuzma (LAL) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
[Observable in enhanced video] Holiday (NOP) splits his feet.
Rondo (LAL) gives Holiday (NOP) room to land on the jump shot attempt.
Payton (NOP) commits a take foul on Bullock (LAL).
